public class VDSObjectManagerAdapter

implements VDSIObjectManagerListener

This class implements VDSIObjectManagerListener and provides default empty method implementations for class create, object create, object update and object delete events raised by a VDSObjectManager object when one or more classes are created, one or more objects are created, updated or deleted respectively. The empty methods must be overridden by objects interested in one or more of the events from a VDSObjectManager object. The intent to let a subclass selectively implement either or both of object create and object delete events that a VDSObjectManager can raise.
